@node "English Words" "Some Words"
@{jcenter} @{b}@{u}Some Words from the Author@{ub}@{uu}
@{jleft}
 First of all thanx for downloading this (at the time) little guide.I hope you
 can understand my English because I can`t speak English very good.As you surely
 recognized this Guide contains Heavy Metal Lyrics.Well I have only put the Lyrics
 of five records in this guide because it`s a lot of work.And why should I write
 the Lyrics of 20 records or more if nobody wants it? Well I will work further on
 this Guide but if I would get response of a lot of people I would work much harder
 on it.You can send me your favourite Lyrics,too.And of course you can tell me what
 I should change,what could be made better,... .I hope I`ll get a lot of response
 from you.
 You can find my adress by clicking @{"here" link "English about"}.
 
@{jright} @{b}@{i}Christopher Jakubeit@{ui}@{ub} 
@{jleft}
 PS: Only the GERMAN TEXTES are legally valid!!
@endnode
@node "English Freeware" "Freeware"
@{jcenter} @{b}@{u}Freeware@{ub}@{uu}
@{jleft}
 This Guide is Freeware.This means you can copy it,if you don`t make any money
 with it.You are only allowed to achieve money for your costs.This Guide can
 pick up on all PD-Series,especially the AMINET CD`s.This Guide can also be put 
 on CoverDisks/Cd`s.But then I will get a littel notice from you.
 If you like this Guide (or not), I will get a letter,e-mail,postcard or what-
 ever,where you say what you like (dislike) and what you would change.
 You can find my Adress and some words about me @{"here" link "English About"}.
@endnode
@node "English About" "Who to hell done this shit?"
@{jcenter} @{b}@{u}About Me@{ub}@{uu}
@{jleft}
 You surely ask yourself who to hell done this shit.Well it started when I 
 found the "HEAVY METAL GUIDE" in the Aminet.I felt in love with this Guide
 and started to write something similar.But I don`t want to copy the "HMG".So
 I listed all my CD`s and the "CD-Guide" was born.You can find this in the 
 Aminet too (docs/hyper).Well after that I started to think what I could do 
 next.I found the Metallica- and Megadeth-Lyrics in the Aminet,and liked it.
 But why should be there two Guides if you can do this in one? And so I started
 to write the Heavy Metal Lyrics Guide.You can see in the "CD-Guide" which CD-
 Lyrics I`m going to add to the Guide.
 And now some words about me.Well I`m 17 Years old and I Live in Germany.I`m 
 in the 10th grade of a grammar shool.I use the Amiga since ca.1990 (then A500;
 now A1200).My hobbies are Soccer,Music (Metal),talk dirty about Boygroups,
 Partys and of course girls.Well you can see I`m almost normal.
 If you have any comments,critics,praise,Materials,found mistakes,... then
 write me.

 My Adress: Christopher Jaubeit
            Grandkuhle 8F
            30823 Garbsen

 Phone:     05137/121163
 e-mail:    chris.jakubeit@t-online.de

 Homepage:  http://members.xoom.com/sizzel/

@endnode
